  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  25 to 55 years old

          -  Good general health

          -  Able to attend all 8 sessions of the course and practice the techniques each night for
             25 minutes

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Psychiatric medications

          -  Significant medical or psychological illness

          -  Metalic implants (such as a pacemaker or artificial joints) that are not MRI
             compatible.

          -  Claustrophobia

          -  Pregnancy

          -  Previous head trauma or neurological disorder

          -  Previous experience with yoga or meditation
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
